  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK256">
<l>tiṉaṟporuṭṭāṟ koḷḷā tulakeṉiṉ yārum</l>
<l>vilaipporuṭṭā lūṉṟaruvā ril</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the world does not destroy life for the purpose of eating, then no one would sell flesh for the sake of money.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
